stories.title: Canada gain consolation win
stories.subTitle: Kenya v Canada, 6th match, ICC Tri Series, Mombasa
stories.summary: Canada pulled off an excellent 69-run win over Kenya, the form team of the tournament, dismissing them for just 144 in the sixth and final match of the ICC Tri Series at Mombasa
